###############################################
# 13. CATATAN PENTING FIELD & BEHAVIOR
###############################################

# ─── SCREENING ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Parameter:
#   cabang  : kode cabang (optional, default All)
#   kdtk    : kode toko (optional, jika ada → Level 3 single store)
#   periode : YYYY-MM (WAJIB)
#
# Response sukses (multi-store):
#   { success, message, screenedStores, activeStores, resolvedStores, taskId }
#
# Response sukses (single store):
#   { success, message, hasIssues, issuesCount }

# ─── RESUME PER SHOP ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Hanya menampilkan toko dengan RECID='*' (ada selisih)
# Toko resolved (RECID='1') tidak muncul
# Kolom sort valid: CAB, KDTK, NAMA, TOTAL_ISSUES, TOTAL_SEL_NET_GL,
#   TOTAL_SEL_NET_CD, TOTAL_SEL_PPN_GL, TOTAL_SEL_PPN_CD, TOTAL_SEL_NET,
#   TOTAL_SEL_PPN, UPDTIME_LATEST

# ─── DETAIL PER TOKO ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Format tanggal di daily[]: YYYY-MM-DD
